column4: So, seems that I've gotten pregnant.
What great news? You've not improved at all, you're as unreliable as ever.
At this point, I'm worrying about the future of my child. Who's going to support us? The baby will have to live with a deadbeat father.
But I'm trying my best here. I am doing better! Just the other day…
Yes, yes, I know. You've been trying. I can see it. I was just teasing you.
But it's not enough. Be better. Otherwise, you're going to get tormented to death by me and our child.
